name: Spirit of the Sonora
description:
Title: Spirit of the Sonora

This is an 8 x 10 archival print from a painting I made in acrylics of a desert spirit with the a rare pronghorn deer.


Print is signed, titled and dated in pencil.

8 x 10 archival print on lightly textured watercolor paper with white space around the image.

Copyright mark is not seen on actual print


S H I P P I N G
Prints are made individually. I try to ship them out within 2-3 business days. Multiple prints are shipped in one sleeve to save on shipping.

For international shipping I fill out a customs form for every international order. The buyer is responsible for any customs fees or duties that might be applicable through their post office.

P A C K I N G
Each print arrives in a clear sleeve with a backing board and is then shipped in a rigid fiberboard mailer.

Thank you for looking!
